                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211024-14-victim170 t18211024-14-viclabel93"></join>. On the 22d of September, I was at the bottom of <placeName id="t18211024-14-crimeloc94">Gold's-hill, Shadwell</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18211024-14-crimeloc94" type="placeName" value="Gold's-hill, Shadwell"></interp>
